thread.title: BRIEF-Teladoc Inc Q4 Loss Per Share $0.76

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Teladoc Inc Q4 Loss Per Share $0.76
text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - Teladoc Inc:
* TELADOC ANNOUNCES FULL YEAR AND FOURTH QUARTER 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 LOSS PER SHARE $0.76 * Q4 REVENUE ROSE 106 PERCENT TO $77.1 MILLION * SEES FY 2018 REVENUE $350 MILLION TO $360 MILLION * SEES Q1 2018 REVENUE $86 MILLION TO $88 MILLION * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $-0.51, REVENUE VIEW $76.2 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q1 REVENUE VIEW $83.8 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* FY2018 REVENUE VIEW $355.9 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
